Ask HN: Dual adjustable arm keyboard setup?
text:
Hi HN, have you ever seen anything like what I'm describing or have ideas for how to build it? Essentially I want to have a fully split keyboard with each side resting on / attached to a tray which is mobile. This way, I can adjust the position of my hands relative to my monitor throughout the day, mitigating "rest is strain".

Thanks in advance.
